    {
      "类型": "method",
      "名称": "exitMasterProcessRole",
      "返回值": "Promise<void>",
      "所属模块": "未知模块",
      "功能描述": "Exit from the master process role of the current process. After calling this method: - System stops triggering `onNewProcessRequest` callbacks on current process. - Process can rejoin candidate pool via `promoteCurrentToCandidateMasterProcess`.",
